# Cloud mode: connect to Render API & DB
# Copy to .env.cloud and set your Render **origin** (with or without trailing /api — both work).
#
VITE_API_URL=https://myshop-api-9pd4.onrender.com

# Or explicitly (same effective URL after proxy normalization):
# VITE_API_URL=https://myshop-api-9pd4.onrender.com/api

# Then run from repo root: npm run dev:pos:cloud  (POS web only, local Vite + cloud API)
# Or build/run desktop against cloud: npm run electron:cloud
